window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Some old flames won't stop smoldering.... </p> <p>Zoe Parker knew better than to play with fire. Fireman Reid Martin sparked a flame in her that she couldn't put out. Will Zoe be able to escape with her heart before she gets burned? </p> <p><i>Cold Flame</i> is the third story in the Deadwood Shorts collection, set between the sixth and seventh books in the Deadwood Mystery Series. </p>"; 
